                 ```bash
                 $MIGRATE_TO_CODEX --validate-target ~/.codex/
                 $MIGRATE_TO_CODEX --validate-target ./.codex/
                 ```

              Run `$MIGRATE_TO_CODEX --help` for flags (`--scan-only`, `--plan`, `--doctor`, `--validate-target`, defaults, and so on). Deep tables and more links are in `references/differences.md`.

