              # Expo Patterns

              SDK: `@clerk/expo` v3+. Requires Expo 53+, React Native 0.73+.

              ## What Do You Need?

              | Task | Reference |
              |------|-----------|
              | Persist tokens with SecureStore | references/token-storage.md |
              | OAuth (Google, Apple, GitHub) | references/oauth-deep-linking.md |
